---
title: Quick Parmesan Beef Rissoles with Cucumber Salad & Fries
description: Give rissoles a bit of flair with our Aussie spice blend, plus Parmesan for an easy flavour boost. With potato fries and a tangy
Italian-dressed salad, this meal shines a whole new light on a tried-and-true dinner.

*Keep an eye out... Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be slightly different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
